15. A material handling system comprising:
(a) a first leg;
(b) a first foot coupled to the first leg;
(c) a second leg;
(d) a second foot coupled to the second leg;
(e) a spacer;
(f) a first stop provided on the spacer;
(g) a second stop provided on the spacer;
